# FactLockCam State & DI Constraints

- FORBID `package:bloc`, `flutter_bloc`, and `package:provider`.
- REQUIRE `flutter_riverpod` for all UI state flowing through `ProviderScope`, `ConsumerWidget`, and `ConsumerStatefulWidget`.
- REQUIRE `get_it` for internal service wiring (composition root: `factlockcam_app/lib/core/di/injection.dart`; `injectable`+codegen optional when build_runner is available).
- ENFORCE bridging pattern: `final vaultServiceProvider = Provider<VaultService>((ref) => getIt<VaultService>());`
- REQUIRE heavy computations (SHA-256, AES-GCM, image thumbnail generation) to execute within `Isolate.run()` (or browser-native Web Crypto / Canvas APIs on web, where isolates are unavailable) to protect UI frame times.
